<br>
He is not that bad.<br>
He does not DT like the other golems and does not even need to be slowed, he is that slow.<br>
So your Tanks will not be droping every minute.<br>
With a good CH rotation on your MT you should be fine.<br>
Fire Lures work best on him.  I was hitting for full when we killed him this week.<br>
Splurt worked good too.  The druid 2k fire spells landed good too.<br>
<br>
If you need another wizard shoot me a tell.<br>
150K does take a long time, Koidacs, bard mana, and mod rods help.<br>
I went oom and had to med to cast more.<br>
<br>
You also want to watch your push when fighting him.<br>
<br>
